If you are having issues with the mod, download this repository and replace the workshop folder with the downloaded one.
Workshop folder can be found at: Location\Steam\steamapps\workshop\content\32470\1880641154.
How to Download: 
1. Click the Green Clone or Download then select Download ZIP.
2. Extract Zip 
3. Replace the Folder the ZIP with the one found above.
4. Profit.
If you are still having issues leave a comment on the steam page or on the Project Gold Discord Server (https://discord.gg/cKfrEX7) in 
#mod-support.
